News.Title: Goldkart Jewels Secures Import License for Gold Dore Bars
News.Summary: Goldkart Jewels has obtained an import license from the Directorate General of Foreign Trade (DGFT), allowing the company to import gold dore bars worth Rs 1,000 crore. This license grants Goldkart Jewels the ability to directly import raw materials for their jewelry production.

News.Title: Goldkart Jewels Secures Import License for Gold Dore Bars
News.Summary: Goldkart Jewels has obtained an import license from the Directorate General of Foreign Trade (DGFT) for importing gold dore bars. The license allows for imports valued at ₹1,000 crore.
